'To be on the spot , I hinted . 
'Just so , said Mrs. Micawber . 
'To be on the spot . 
But , the truth is , talent is not wanted in the Custom House . 
The local influence of my family was quite unavailing to obtain any employment in that department , for a man of Mr. Micawber's abilities . 
They would rather NOT have a man of Mr. Micawber's abilities . 
He would only show the deficiency of the others . 
In fact , said Mrs. Micawber , lowering her voice , 'this is between ourselves our reception was cool . 
'Dear me ! I said . 
'Yes , said Mrs. Micawber . 
