From this employment she suddenly desisted , and said to Steerforth , much to my confusion 'Who's your friend ? 'Mr . 
Copperfield , said Steerforth 'he wants to know you . 
'Face like a peach ! standing on tiptoe to pinch my cheek as I sat . 
'Quite tempting ! I'm very fond of peaches . 
