Now that , my child , continued Miss Mowcher , rubbing all the time as busily as ever , 'is another instance of the refreshing humbug I was speaking of . 
I say I do a little in that way myself . 
One Dowager , SHE calls it lip salve . 
Another , SHE calls it gloves . 
Another , SHE calls it tucker edging . 
Another , SHE calls it a fan . 
I call it whatever THEY call it . 
