Think twice , before it goes over you . 
Think twice , you , Micawber , if you don't want to be crushed . 
I recommend you to take yourself off , and be talked to presently , you fool ! while there's time to retreat . 
Where's mother ? he said , suddenly appearing to notice , with alarm , the absence of Traddles , and pulling down the bell rope . 
'Fine doings in a person's own house ! 'Mrs . 
Heep is here , sir , said Traddles , returning with that worthy mother of a worthy son . 
